<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4581578>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Metaphire yuanpoaea. (A) Male pore region (op, oval pad; sw, skin wall); (B) caecum; (C) spermathecae (dv, diverticulum; amp, ampulla); (D) testis sacs and seminal vesicles (ts, testis sacs; sv, seminal vesicles); (E) prostate gland." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4581578/files/figure.png" .

